459
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:47,360
Sautéed potato, green pepper and eggplant.
Stewed chicken with mushroom.

460
00:37:48,010 --> 00:37:49,170
Eat more, Ms Ma.

461
00:37:50,160 --> 00:37:54,480
You... Why are you dressed up...

462
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:57,320
