472
00:38:48,510 --> 00:38:49,510
You eat.

473
00:38:52,890 --> 00:38:53,920
I get it now.

474
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:55,440
Is it because

475
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:57,160
